summaries.short: The Mikes showcase their special talents for a cinematic performance in the desert, but dramatic events bring real-life consequences to the competition.
summaries.full: The stakes are higher than ever for the remaining Mikes, who are tasked with prepping for their rawest performance yet. In a week that’s all about connection, breaking the rules brings costly consequences for one contestant, and some unforeseen events leave the Mikes reeling.

summaries.short: A look back at the highlights from episode 4 of Finding Magic Mike.
summaries.full: A look back at the highlights from episode 4 of Finding Magic Mike.

summaries.short: After a sensual lap dance number for special guest Amanda Seales, the remaining Mikes perform in the sexiest number yet for a spot in the finale.
summaries.full: Special guest Amanda Seales is on hand as the Final Four put their lap dance skills to the test… in underwear. After a tough elimination, the last three Mikes get wet and wild in one of the most sexual and challenging performances yet: The Water Dance.

summaries.short: The Mikes partner with female dancers for a 1950’s drive-in performance meant to highlight their charisma, and Nicole Scherzinger offers advice before a shocking elimination round.
summaries.full: Before partnering with female dancers for a “nifty” 1950s-inspired performance, the Mikes have 90 seconds to share a memorable story for an intimate focus group – but end up baring a little too much. While the Mikes turn up the charisma, Nicole Scherzinger drops by to offer advice and help the Creative Team decide who goes home.

summaries.short: A look back at the highlights from episode 5 of Finding Magic Mike.
summaries.full: A look back at the highlights from episode 5 of Finding Magic Mike.

summaries.short: The final two bring their A-game alongside the Magic Mike Live pros to deliver a truly magical performance that will determine who walks away with the $100,000 prize.
summaries.full: The competition is stiff as the final two must learn over ten routines in just five days for a performance with the Magic Mike Live pros. After comedian Nikki Glaser drops by to show her appreciation, the finalists take a moment to recognize how far they’ve come before a grand finale that’s full of surprises.

summaries.short: A look back at the highlights from episode 3 of Finding Magic Mike.
summaries.full: A look back at the highlights from episode 3 of Finding Magic Mike.

summaries.short: A sexy suit dance and a focus group with Whitney Cummings separates the men from the boys before an elimination that sends one of them packing.
summaries.full: It’s time to separate the men from the boys as the Mikes embrace their attractiveness, inside and out, in a sexy suit dance on the Magic Mike Live stage. At a focus group and Q&A hosted by comedian Whitney Cummings, the competitors get candid – but the winner’s reward may be even more revealing.

summaries.full: A look back at the highlights from episode 2 of Finding Magic Mike.

summaries.short: Confidence is key as the ten “Mikes” take their shirts off for an unlikely crowd and prepare for a rooftop pool party performance, with help from special guest Robin Thede.
summaries.full: The competition heats up as the ten Mikes take a field trip to show off some suave moves to a group of ladies who aren’t what they expected. Later, comedian and special guest Robin Thede stops by for an epic rooftop pool party performance – which leads to the first elimination.
